  <entry>
    <title>kali linux安装后的初步配置</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2017/03/13/kali-linux-configuration/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2017/03/13/kali-linux-configuration/</id>
    <published>2017-03-13T13:35:40.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-03-16T14:26:36.031Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="配置apt源文件"><a href="#配置apt源文件" class="headerlink" title="配置apt源文件"></a>配置apt源文件</h1><ul>
<li><p>修改源文件</p>
<figure class="highlight vala"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="meta"># vi /etc/apt/sources.list</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<p>#deb cdrom:[Debian GNU/Linux 2016.1 <em>Kali-rolling</em> - Official Snapshot amd64 LIVE/INSTALL Binary 20160830-16:34]/ kali-rolling contrib main non-free<br>#deb cdrom:[Debian GNU/Linux 2016.1 <em>Kali-rolling</em> - Official Snapshot amd64 LIVE/INSTALL Binary 20160830-16:34]/ kali-rolling contrib main non-free<br>deb <a href="http://http.kali.org/kali" target="_blank" rel="external">http://http.kali.org/kali</a> kali-rolling main non-free contrib<br>deb-src <a href="http://http.kali.org/kali" target="_blank" rel="external">http://http.kali.org/kali</a> kali-rolling main non-free contrib<br>deb <a href="http://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/kali" target="_blank" rel="external">http://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/kali</a> kali-rolling main non-free contrib<br>deb <a href="http://mirrors.neusoft.edu.cn/kali" target="_blank" rel="external">http://mirrors.neusoft.edu.cn/kali</a> kali-rolling main non-free contrib<br>deb <a href="http://repo.kali.org/kali" target="_blank" rel="external">http://repo.kali.org/kali</a> kali-rolling main non-free contrib</p>
</blockquote>
</li>
</ul>
<h1 id="对linux-进行更新"><a href="#对linux-进行更新" class="headerlink" title="对linux 进行更新"></a>对linux 进行更新</h1><ul>
<li>对安装的kali linux 清除安装包缓存、更新apt-get源文件、软件升级和发行版升级执行命令<figure class="highlight processing"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"># apt-<span class="built_in">get</span> clean &amp;&amp; apt-<span class="built_in">get</span> update &amp;&amp; apt-<span class="built_in">get</span> upgrade &amp;&amp; apt-<span class="built_in">get</span> <span class="built_in">dist</span>-upgrade -y</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<h1 id="解决没有声音问题"><a href="#解决没有声音问题" class="headerlink" title="解决没有声音问题"></a>解决没有声音问题</h1><ul>
<li>pulsseaudio 无法识别内置网卡的问题，将pulseaudio 进行重装，执行命令：<figure class="highlight brainfuck"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment">#</span> <span class="comment">apt</span><span class="literal">-</span><span class="comment">get</span> <span class="literal">-</span><span class="literal">-</span><span class="comment">purge</span> <span class="literal">-</span><span class="literal">-</span><span class="comment">reinstall</span> <span class="comment">install</span> <span class="comment">pulseaudio</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<h1 id="添加用户"><a href="#添加用户" class="headerlink" title="添加用户"></a>添加用户</h1><ul>
<li><p>新建用户user并指定用户的家目录为/home</p>
<figure class="highlight vala"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="meta"># useradd -m user</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>设置密码</p>
<figure class="highlight vala"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="meta"># passwd user</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>-a 附加组 -G 指定一个群组 或者多个群组</p>
<figure class="highlight apache"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment"># usermod -a -G sudo user</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>将用户的shell改为bash</p>
<figure class="highlight vala"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="meta"># chsh -s /bin/bash user</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<h1 id="安装filezilla-客户端"><a href="#安装filezilla-客户端" class="headerlink" title="安装filezilla 客户端"></a>安装filezilla 客户端</h1><figure class="highlight armasm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"># apt-<span class="meta">get</span> install filezilla filezilla-<span class="meta">common</span> -y</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h1 id="安装Recordmydesktop桌面记录工具和Remina远程客户端"><a href="#安装Recordmydesktop桌面记录工具和Remina远程客户端" class="headerlink" title="安装Recordmydesktop桌面记录工具和Remina远程客户端"></a>安装Recordmydesktop桌面记录工具和Remina远程客户端</h1><figure class="highlight vala"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="meta"># apt-get install gtk-recordmydesktop recordmydesktop remmina -y</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h1 id="启动用户自动登录"><a href="#启动用户自动登录" class="headerlink" title="启动用户自动登录"></a>启动用户自动登录</h1><figure class="highlight vala"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="meta"># vi /etc/lightdm/lightdm.conf</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<p>将pam-service = lightdm和pam-autologin-service=lightdm-autologin取消注释<br>取消autologin-user = username注释，并修改为想要登录的用户名</p>
</blockquote>
<p>将用户 user 加入 autologin 组<br><figure class="highlight vala"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="meta"># groupadd autologin</span></div><div class="line"><span class="meta"># gpasswd -a user autologin</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h1 id="解决以太网“设备无法托管”的错误"><a href="#解决以太网“设备无法托管”的错误" class="headerlink" title="解决以太网“设备无法托管”的错误"></a>解决以太网“设备无法托管”的错误</h1><figure class="highlight vala"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="meta"># vi /etc/NetworkManager/NetworkManager.conf</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<p>managed=false 修改为 managed=true</p>
</blockquote>
<h1 id="安装tor"><a href="#安装tor" class="headerlink" title="安装tor"></a>安装tor</h1><figure class="highlight actionscript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ sudo apt-<span class="keyword">get</span> install tor</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><a href="https://www.torproject.org/projects/torbrowser.html.en" target="_blank" rel="external">tor官网下载tor</a><br><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ tar -xvJf tor-browser-linux64-<span class="number">6.5</span>.<span class="number">1</span>_zh-CN<span class="selector-class">.tar</span><span class="selector-class">.xz</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h1 id="安装shdowsocks"><a href="#安装shdowsocks" class="headerlink" title="安装shdowsocks"></a>安装shdowsocks</h1><h2 id="安装libqtshadowsocks-dev"><a href="#安装libqtshadowsocks-dev" class="headerlink" title="安装libqtshadowsocks-dev"></a>安装libqtshadowsocks-dev</h2><ul>
<li><p>下载 libqtshadowsocks-dev 源码</p>
<figure class="highlight crmsh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ git <span class="keyword">clone</span> <span class="title">https</span>://github.com/shadowsocks/libQtShadowsocks.git</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>安装依赖</p>
<figure class="highlight q"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ sudo apt-<span class="built_in">get</span> install qtbase5-<span class="built_in">dev</span> qt5-qmake qt5-default libbotan1<span class="number">.10</span>-<span class="built_in">dev</span>  libqrencode-<span class="built_in">dev</span> Zlibappindicator-<span class="built_in">dev</span> libzbar-<span class="built_in">dev</span> unzip debhelper</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>编译和打包</p>
<figure class="highlight elixir"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="variable">$ </span>cd libQtShadowsocks</div><div class="line"><span class="variable">$ </span>qmake &amp;&amp; make</div><div class="line"><span class="variable">$ </span>dpkg-buildpackage -uc -us -b</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>安装</p>
<figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ cd ..</div><div class="line">$ sudo dpkg -<span class="selector-tag">i</span> libqtshadowsocks_1.<span class="number">10.0</span>-<span class="number">1</span>_amd64<span class="selector-class">.deb</span></div><div class="line">$ sudo dpkg -<span class="selector-tag">i</span> shadowsocks-libqtshadowsocks_1.<span class="number">10.0</span>-<span class="number">1</span>_amd64<span class="selector-class">.deb</span></div><div class="line">$ sudo dpkg -<span class="selector-tag">i</span> libqtshadowsocks-dev_1.<span class="number">10.0</span>-<span class="number">1</span>_amd64.deb</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="安装-shadowsocks-qt5"><a href="#安装-shadowsocks-qt5" class="headerlink" title="安装 shadowsocks-qt5"></a>安装 shadowsocks-qt5</h2><ul>
<li><p>下载 shadowsocks-qt5 源码</p>
<figure class="highlight crmsh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ git <span class="keyword">clone</span> <span class="title">https</span>://github.com/shadowsocks/shadowsocks-qt5.git</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>安装依赖</p>
<figure class="highlight q"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">sudo apt-<span class="built_in">get</span> install libQtShadowsocks-<span class="built_in">dev</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>编译和打包</p>
<figure class="highlight elixir"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="variable">$ </span>cd shadowsocks-qt5</div><div class="line"><span class="variable">$ </span>qmake &amp;&amp; make</div><div class="line"><span class="variable">$ </span>sudo dpkg-buildpackage -uc -us -b</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>安装</p>
<figure class="highlight lsl"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ cd ..</div><div class="line">$ dpkg -i shadowsocks-qt5_2<span class="number">.8</span><span class="number">.0</span><span class="number">-1</span>_amd64.deb</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
